HEADWORD: Shadoof
<hw>Sha*doof"</hw> <pr>(sh⟦adot⟧*d⟦oomac⟧f")</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[Ar. <ets>sh⟦amac⟧d⟦umac⟧f</ets>.]</ety> <def>A machine, resembling
